      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for those prioritizing function over form. While the engine and transmission are operational and it handles well on the road, the car shows clear signs of its age, including visible exterior blemishes and some wear on the interior upholstery. It has been maintained to stay roadworthy, but a buyer should expect minor cosmetic imperfections and the typical mechanical character of a high-mileage vehicle. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation.",
