      "description": "Looking for your next project or a budget-friendly fixer-upper? This car is ready for a new owner with a vision! While it definitely shows its age and will need some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its best, it offers a fantastic foundation for anyone who loves to roll up their sleeves. It's an honest car at a great price, perfect for a mechanic's special or a dedicated restoration project!",
