    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute beauty, and let me tell you, it is in truly incredible shape! It's been pampered, garage-kept, and honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents\u2014just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
